use intelliJ ultimate or cmd line, run index.js located in server/index.js
//to run in cmd:
// cd to server folder
// run: node index.js

launch desktopLauncher and create a new game, enable multiplayer
launch desktopLauncher again and join game created by first player
enter the ip address or localhost port it will display a copy of the world and information

use "set DEBUG=*" in the cmd in the server dir to see all debug messages
this must be done before the server is started and does not work in intelliJ ultimate